snippet.title: Lazerball Gameplay Trailer | New Multiplayer Dodgeball Brawler!
snippet.description:
Lazerball is a fast paced, multiplayer sports brawler game!
Aim and curve the ball with precision and show off your dodgeball skills!


There are multiple characters, stages and DJs to choose from, 
as well as different game modes including:
- Original lives
- Marksman
- Points Attack
- Goal Scoring


Lazerball Steam Link:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1888270/Lazerball/


Wishlish the game if you want to be notified when Lazerball releases!
